 cookie.Domain = "https://contoso.com";
 new CookieContainer().Add(cookie);
 ```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a1751-141">但是，有了这些特殊字符转义以下构造函数将创建<xref:System.Net.Cookie>，它可以添加到<xref:System.Net.CookieContainer>实例：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a1751-141">However, the following constructor with these special characters escaped will create a <xref:System.Net.Cookie> that can be added to a <xref:System.Net.CookieContainer> instance:</span></span>  
 
 ```csharp
